headline: Atmos Energy (ATO) Reports Strong Q3 Earnings and Raises 2025 Guidance
summary: Atmos Energy (ATO) announced its third-quarter earnings results on August 6, 2025, showcasing a healthy increase in sales and net income compared to the previous year. The company also raised its earnings guidance for 2025, signaling confidence in its future financial performance. Additionally, Atmos Energy affirmed a quarterly dividend of 87 cents per share, marking its 167th consecutive quarterly dividend.
